text: AC8 or AC-8 may refer to: * USS Neptune (AC-8), a US Navy collier ship active during World War I * Comte AC-8, a 1930s Swiss six-seat light transport aircraft * Southern Pacific class AC-8, a model of steam locomotive * AC-8, an IEC Utilization Category * Assassin's Creed Odyssey, an action-adventure video game, the eighth main game in the Assassin's Creed series
title: AC8
